    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4557366/" class="title-link">只能叫的狗</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4557366"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bravowan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u35356138-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bravowan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">柳远</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-31"
      class="main-meta">2010-12-31 13:26:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4557366_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      汪汪！汪汪汪！     写杂文的人在中国就像一条狗。看上去凶神恶煞，呲着黄牙，吐着粉红色的舌头，瞪着浑浊的眼睛喘着粗气。却从来没有真正咬过人，只能“汪汪……”叫个不停。     二三十年前那些人写文章骂得那些社会现象现在依然存在，经久不衰；二三十年前那些人写文章...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4557366/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
